{"tid":2064592,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"庫德洛：美經濟或呈強勁V型復甦 下半年經濟或增兩成","createTime":"2020-06-15T02:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T03:44:11.000Z","uid":166360,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce84f951bf02b02ca5ad45621907b52defa91ae5","tid":2064592,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:32:35.000Z","msg":"庫德洛：美經濟或呈強勁V型復甦 下半年經濟或增兩成<br />\n3小時前<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國白宮經濟顧問庫德洛預料，美國經濟很可能出現非常強勁的V型復甦。<br />\n<br />\n庫德洛接受電視台訪問，他不認同聯儲局主席鮑威爾上周對美國經濟較為審慎的展望。庫德洛稱，美國政府對經濟從疫情中復甦樂觀，預料美國經濟將會出現強勁的V型反彈，下半年經濟有望增長20%，年底前失業率將降至10%以下。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=394445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394445&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8u6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=729fda6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394445&h=70443907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=394445</a>"},{"pid":"518e2d07302acf8284d08e04dc5988fb2d87bedf","tid":2064592,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:43:55.000Z","msg":"養懶哂d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e498a3dfac65ad15d51c75307937088d5bf147","tid":2064592,"uid":134415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:49:58.000Z","msg":"翻譯: Trump要連任"},{"pid":"686c8d123a9126083565e21c0bc385de80bb845f","tid":2064592,"uid":356101,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30e498a3dfac65ad15d51c75307937088d5bf147","tid":2064592,"uid":134415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:49:58.000Z","msg":"翻譯: Trump要連任"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T03:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /